question.en:
Consider the following PL/SQL code snippet:<br><pre><code>DECLARE
    total NUMBER := 0;
BEGIN
    FOR i IN 1..5 LOOP
        total := total + i;
    END LOOP;
END;</code></pre> What will be the final value of total?

